description:
Barcelona and PSG are scheduled to play in the UEFA Champions League quarter-finals on April 10 and April 16, 2024.

This market will resolve to "Barcelona" if Barcelona advances to the semi-finals of the UEFA Champions League by winning their tie against PSG. 

This market will resolve to "PSG" if PSG advances to the semi-finals of the UEFA Champions League by winning their tie against Barcelona. 

If the tie between Barcelona and PSG is postponed to a date before June 1, 2024, this market's timeframe will extend to the new match dates. If the tie is canceled, or postponed to a date in June or later, this market will resolve immediately to "50-50".

This market may be resolved immediately upon the completion of the second leg of the tie.
